NDL-DC 13pp927 01-Utagawa Kunisada-奴凧平 市川市蔵・夢想兵衛 下り中村鶴助-文久2-crd.jpg|{{ill|Ukiyo-e|ja|浮世絵|12=draft}} "Yakko Takobei" (奴凧平) (from 'Toyokuni Album', late Edo period){{Efn|In the ukiyo-e, kabuki actor {{ill|Ichikawa Shisō|ja|市川市蔵|12=draft}} mimics a yakko kite, suspended for an acrobatic performance.}}
