Image:Odori023.jpg|Participant portraying {{ill|Watōnai|ja|和藤内|12=draft}} from {{ill|The Battles of Coxinga|ja|国性爺合戦|12=draft}}. (Tiger Dance, Yokosuka City)
</gallery>

